  "title": "Packaging Operator",
  "description": "<p><strong>HAID BIOTECHNOLOGY INDUSTRY (SINGAPORE) PTE. LTD. </strong>is seeking a detail-oriented and experienced Warehouse Operations Executive<strong> </strong>to join our new startup team in Singapore. The ideal candidate will be overseeing and optimizing the end-to-end warehouse operations, ensuring efficiency, accuracy, and safety in all processes.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p>1.    Ensure timely replenishment of packaging materials\n(e.g., bags, label paper, stretch film) for the fully automated packaging line.</p><p>2.    Perform basic mechanical troubleshooting for the\npackaging equipment.</p><p>3.    Maintain cleanliness of the work area and strictly\nadhere to production safety and food hygiene standards.</p><p>4.    Complete other related production tasks assigned by\nthe supervisor.</p><p><strong>Important Requirement:</strong></p><p>Candidates\nmust not have acrophobia (fear of heights), as the job may occasionally involve\nusing a ladder to changeover products.</p><p><strong>Job\nRequirements</strong></p><p><strong>Age /\nPhysical:</strong> Good health and capable\nof performing physical labor.  <br />\n<strong>Experience:</strong> No prior experience required;\non-the-job training will be provided. Experience in manufacturing or food\nprocessing plants is advantageous.<br />\n<strong>Attitude:</strong> Hard-working and diligent, responsible,\nable to follow work instructions, and possess good teamwork spirit.<br />\n<strong>Other:</strong> Able to adapt to working environments that\nmay involve<strong> dust and noise</strong>, as\ncommonly found in feed production.</p><p><strong>Language:\nGood command Mandarin</strong> to liaise with Mandarin-speaking business associates.</p><p>• Company website: https://www.haid.com.cn/</p>",
